text: James Randell (4 August 1880 - 7 December 1952) was an Australian cricketer. He played nine first-class matches for New South Wales between 1909/10 and 1924/25. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1880 births Category:1952 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
